data.description: Solid ranch home with newer furnance and water heater. This home has been very well cared for and is move in ready. The home does need some updates, which are reflected in the price but everything is in working order. Washer and dryer are included in the price. There's also a good sized yard, 2 car garage and storage shed. Property has no known defects but is being sold "AS IS". **Hard/private money loan offers accepted ONLY with bank statement POF in purchaser's name for 30% of entire project
